  "body": "Output of `helm version`:\r\n```\r\nClient: &version.Version{SemVer:\"v2.9.1\", GitCommit:\"20adb27c7c5868466912eebdf6664e7390ebe710\", GitTreeState:\"clean\"}\r\nServer: &version.Version{SemVer:\"v2.9.1\", GitCommit:\"20adb27c7c5868466912eebdf6664e7390ebe710\", GitTreeState:\"clean\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\nOutput of `kubectl version`:\r\n\r\n```\r\nClient Version: version.Info{Major:\"1\", Minor:\"10\", GitVersion:\"v1.10.5\", GitCommit:\"32ac1c9073b132b8ba18aa830f46b77dcceb0723\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", BuildDate:\"2018-06-21T11:46:00Z\", GoVersion:\"go1.9.3\", Compiler:\"gc\", Platform:\"darwin/amd64\"}\r\nServer Version: version.Info{Major:\"1\", Minor:\"10\", GitVersion:\"v1.10.5\", GitCommit:\"32ac1c9073b132b8ba18aa830f46b77dcceb0723\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", BuildDate:\"2018-06-21T11:34:22Z\", GoVersion:\"go1.9.3\", Compiler:\"gc\", Platform:\"linux/amd64\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\nCloud Provider/Platform (AKS, GKE, Minikube etc.): \r\nkops 1.9.1 on AWS\r\n\r\nExample: https://github.com/nicdoye/helm-set-vs-reuse/tree/set-values-break-upgrades/helm/parent\r\n(Note this is the `parent` chart in `set-values-break-upgrades` tag).\r\n\r\nThe parent chart requires the subchart, `subchart` conditionally on `subchart.enabled` equal `\"true\"`. \r\n\r\nUpgrading the parent *without* adding `--set subchart.enabled=\"true\"` (or `\"false\"`) to the upgrade line fails.\r\n\r\n```console\r\n$ helm install helm/parent --set subchart.enabled=\"true\" -n two-levels\r\nNAME:   two-levels\r\n...\r\n$ helm upgrade two-levels helm/parent --reuse-values\r\nError: UPGRADE FAILED: yaml: line 4: could not find expected ':'\r\n```\r\n",
